{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292860/extras/1Story.png?t=1726590173\" /><br><br>For Evelyn is an intriguing tale of love, betrayal, and the ultimate sacrifice. <br><br>The story takes us into the fantasy world of Aura, a place of magic and mysteries. It has been about 700 years since Arcanbreak, a cataclysmic event that changed the world forever.<br><br>You'll be playing as Yohanna, Evelyn's mother. She\u2019s a strong-willed character, and throughout the game, she will realize how far she is willing to go to protect the ones she loves. With emotional backstories and a powerful, moving musical score, For Evelyn will draw the player in and refuse to let go.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292860/extras/2Features.png?t=1726590173\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story-driven adventure </li><li>Well written, partly voiced narrative </li><li>Original Soundtrack </li><li>Light RPG elements </li><li>Point &amp; Click interaction </li><li>Turn-based battles  </li><li>Retro pixel art graphics </li><li>Unique character portraits </li><li>Varied maps to explore </li><li>Crafting</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292860/extras/3Note.png?t=1726590173\" /><br><br>For Evelyn started development in summer 2019, and has gone through several revisions as I've received constructive feedback and have gotten more experience making games. It has been a passion project for me, and I'm doing my best to make it an enjoyable experience for anyone who enjoys story-driven games. Currently, there are many more stories I've planned to bring to you in the coming years. Thank you all who have supported the creation of For Evelyn!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Completionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1292